<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>メッセージボード</title>
    <!-- CSS only -->
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <script>
      function setId() {
        let id = document.querySelector('#id_input').value
        localStorage.setItem('id', id)
        location.href = '/'
      }
    </script>
  </head>
  <body class="container">
    <header>
      <h1 class="display-4">メッセージボード</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="main">
      <p>あなたのログインネームを入力してください。</p>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="id_input">Login name:</label>
        <input type="text" id="id_input" class="form-control" />
      </div>
      <button onclick="setId()" class="btn btn-primary">送信</button>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
